# Addiction Interventions — Design System

## Brand Colors
```
Sage accent:    #8FAC87   — CTAs, eyebrows, icons, star ratings, checkmarks
Sage deep:      #507969   — italic emphasis in headings, icon hover states
Sage hover:     #6F8E68   — button hover
Dark sage:      #3E5B50   — dark section backgrounds (About, CTA, Process strip)
Cream:          #F5F3E7   — alternating section backgrounds
Cream border:   #EFEFEF   — card borders, dividers
Body text:      #4B4B4B   — paragraph text on light backgrounds
Ink:            #1A1A17   — headings and primary text
White:          #FFFFFF   — section backgrounds, card fills
```

## Section Background Rhythm
Alternate sections using this pattern to create visual cadence:
1. White → 2. Cream (#F5F3E7) → 3. Dark sage (#3E5B50) → repeat
Dark sage sections always use white/sage text. Never use the old #3a5c3c.

## Typography
- **Heading font**: `font-heading` class → Playfair Display (loaded as `--font-playfair`)
- **Body font**: Montserrat (`--font-montserrat`)
- Headings: `font-bold` (700) with `letter-spacing: -0.01em`
- Italic emphasis word inside headings: `<span className="italic text-[#507969]">word</span>` (on light bg) or `<span className="italic text-[#8FAC87]">word</span>` (on dark bg)
- Eyebrows: `<p className="brand-eyebrow mb-3 text-[#8FAC87]">Label</p>` — all caps, 0.05em tracking
- H1 on hero: text-5xl → md:text-6xl → lg:text-7xl, font-bold
- H2 section headings: text-4xl → md:text-5xl, font-bold
- H3 card headings: text-lg → text-xl, font-bold

## Layout Container
```tsx
const CONTAINER = "mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10";
```
Use this for every section. Never mix max-w-5xl or max-w-6xl on new pages.

