## Cards (light section)
Rounded-3xl, white bg, ring-1 ring-[#EFEFEF] or border border-[#EFEFEF]:
```tsx
className="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-[#EFEFEF]"
```
Tiled grid with alternating fill (for service grids):
```tsx
<div className="grid gap-px overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[#EFEFEF] bg-[#EFEFEF] sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
  {/* odd cells: bg-white, even cells: bg-[#F5F3E7]/70 */}
</div>
```

## Decorative Circles (for dark sections)
```tsx
<div className="pointer-events-none absolute -right-32 -top-32 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-[#507969]/40" />
<div className="pointer-events-none absolute -left-20 bottom-0 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-[#8FAC87]/15" />
```
Add `relative overflow-hidden` to the section.

## Floating Stat Card (on images)
```tsx
<div className="absolute -bottom-5 -right-5 rounded-2xl bg-[#3E5B50] px-6 py-5 shadow-xl">
  <p className="font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-white">1,500+</p>
  <p className="mt-0.5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[#8FAC87]">Families Helped</p>
</div>
```

## Page Hero (non-homepage)
Dark sage overlay on a full-width image, content left-aligned:
- eyebrow in #8FAC87
- H1 with italic emphasis word
- Body paragraph
- Primary + secondary CTA
- Trust bullet strip below (`items-center gap-8` row of icon + text)
For pages without an approved AI image, use a cream background with dark text instead.

## PageHero Component Usage Pattern
```tsx
<PageHero
  eyebrow="Intervention Services"
  headline="Alcohol Abuse Interventions"
  italicWord="Alcohol"        // wraps first matching word in italic + #507969
  body="..."
/>
```

## Process Steps Style
4 steps in a dark sage section (#3E5B50), circle icons with numbered badge,
horizontal connector line on desktop (via absolute positioned div).

## Star Ratings
```tsx
{Array.from({ length: 5 }).map((_, i) => (
  <i key={i} className="ri-star-fill text-[#8FAC87] text-sm"></i>
))}
```

## Logo
- Navbar/footer: `NAV_LOGO_URL` in `src/data/site.ts` (Supabase `brand_wordmark_navbar_v4.png`); use `NAV_LOGO_BOX` / `FOOTER_LOGO_BOX` with `fill` + `object-contain` (wide box ~260–340px — do not size by height alone on 4:3 assets)
- Footer: same asset with `brightness-0 invert` for white-on-dark rendering

