## Icons
Remix Icon 4.6.0 via CDN (already loaded in layout.tsx). Class pattern: `ri-*-line` or `ri-*-fill`.
Common icons used in this app:
- ri-phone-fill / ri-phone-line
- ri-check-line (checklist)
- ri-star-fill (ratings)
- ri-shield-check-line (trust)
- ri-map-pin-2-line (location)
- ri-award-line (accreditation)
- ri-time-line (availability)
- ri-arrow-right-line (links)
- ri-heart-pulse-line, ri-medal-2-line, ri-family-line (why-us cards)
